<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.9.7">
<l>cīrtaḻaitta katirccennel ceṅkamalat tiṭaiyiṭaiyiṉ</l>
<l>pārtaḻaittuk karumpōṅkip payaṉviḷaikkun tirunaṟaiyūr</l>
<l>kārtaḻaitta tiruvuruvaṉ kaṇṇapirāṉ viṇṇavarkōṉ</l>
<l>tārtaḻaitta tuḻāymuṭiyaṉ taḷiraṭiyē yaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirunaṟaiyūr where sugarcane produces juice, growing high,</l>
<l>Flourishing in the earth here and there in-between red lotuses</l>
<l rend="indent">and red paddy with fine, flourishing stalks,</l>
<l>O heart, take refuge at the sprout[-like] feet of the one on whose crown is tulasī</l>
<l rend="indent">where flowers flourish,</l>
<l>The one on whose divine form darkness flourishes, lord Kaṇṇaṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent">the celestials’ king.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
